criteria.inclusion_criteria:
1. HLA-haploidentical HSCT patients did not occured GVHD; 
2. Age between 18 to 60;
3. KPS score > 60;
4. No serious organ dysfunction;
5. Expected survival > 3 months.

criteria.exclusion_criteria:
1. Have serious organ dysfunction;
2. Combined with other cancer need treatment;
3. Presence of clinical signs of brain dysfuntion or severe mental illness can not comply with the study protocol;
4. Can not scheduled follow-up;
5. Can not guarantee the completion of the treatment plan and the necessary follow-up observation.
